profile: As a man who grew up with a father that knew how to fix darn near anything, I've become a Man who can fix Darn near anything. I have worked for multiple Interior Design/Decorators from a very young age Teaching me the value of quality and integrity in all things. After High School I worked my way through College with Contractors, Upholsterers as well as helping on a few farms and ranches in the greater Calgary Area. After a short time in the Royal Reserves, I found myself again being the guy that was called to help out with various home, farm, and other jobs that needed someone who knew how to get things done properly and efficiently. I have extensive experience in Furniture building/repair, home maintenance/repair, appliance installation (can repair some appliances) and yard maintenance and landscaping. I've helped out on many farm/ranch operations from a small child helping my grandfather to helping friends in high school and college on their parents farms to current still helping those in need of a helping hand. I D have my son's come help if you're looking for general labour, Farm help, snow removal, Junk clean up and other nonskilled help.
services: Upholstery repair, Home maintenance/repairs, Yard maintenance and landscaping, Farm/Ranch help, General home, yard maintenance, Farm help, Snow shoveling/removal.
